name: Collectibles Meta Map, The Era of Queen of the Abyss
description:
The Era of Queen of the Abyss.
Stage 1: The birth of the first cult members & the gargle
Stage 2: The birth of the children of the cult and the construction of the temple
Stage 3: Creatures af Brockbrock
Stage 4: Those Who Gargle
Stage 5: Down there
Stage 6: Queen of the Abyss

Possible parallel events and overlapping dimensions (surprise drops):
Flashes of memory of sold out cult members' life before the cult
Pets by Brockbrock
The discovery of hidden passages under the temple
And probably more
